SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT a.isn, a.eo2_isn, b.name2, b.name3, b.name4, b.long_name FROM relations AS a INNER JOIN eo AS b ON a.eo2_isn = b.isn WHERE (a.eo1_isn = :1) :2 :3 AND (a.relation_subtype = 20) AND (a.status = 1)
SELECT COUNT(a.eo2_isn) AS Expr2 FROM relations AS a INNER JOIN eo AS b ON a.eo2_isn = b.isn WHERE (a.eo1_isn = :1) :2 :3 AND (a.relation_subtype = 20) AND (a.status = 1)
